      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You've heard the pitch a thousand times: \"Dropship from anywhere, sell everything, make money while you sleep.\" Most of those pitches leave out the messy parts — slow shipping from overseas, flimsy products, refund nightmares. Spocket exists to fix exactly those problems.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Spocket is a dropshipping marketplace that focuses on suppliers based in the United States and Europe. Instead of scraping random catalogs from the far corners of the internet, you get a curated library of products from vetted vendors, ready to connect to your Shopify or WooCommerce store in minutes. The app has earned over 15,000 reviews and holds the #1 spot among dropshipping apps on Shopify — and there are real reasons for that.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-spocket"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Below, I'll walk you through concrete Spocket use cases so you can see whether it fits your business. If you want the full walkthrough first, check out ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "what Spocket actually is",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " on TonyCiencia.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case #1: Launching a Shopify Store With Zero Inventory Risk",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's say you have a product idea — minimalist home décor, pet accessories, eco-friendly kitchen tools — but you don't want to buy 500 units from a factory sight unseen. Spocket solves this from minute one.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You install the Spocket app on Shopify, browse their catalog of over 20 million products, and import the ones you like with a single click. Each listing pulls in product images, descriptions, variants, and pricing. You set your markup, publish the product, and it's live on your store.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No warehouse. No upfront bulk orders. No packaging tape.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When a customer places an order, Spocket forwards it to the supplier automatically. The supplier ships it — typically from a US or EU warehouse — and your customer gets it in 2–7 business days instead of the 2–6 weeks that characterize many overseas suppliers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This use case is perfect for first-time store owners who want to test a niche without committing thousands of dollars to inventory. You validate demand with real orders, learn what your audience actually buys, and scale from there.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://get.spocket.co/2o23w70b1d5w"
